Second Department,

February, 1951.

(February 5, 1951.) Anthony R. Adorno, as Assignee of Mary Adorno, Appellant, v. Vincent Del Borrello, Defendant, and Vin-Del Contracting Co., Inc., Respondent.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Appellate Division denied, with $10 costs. Present — Nolan, P. J., Carswell, Adel, Sneed and MaeCrate, JJ.
